OWNER_NAME: Nova Scotia Department of Natural Resources
STANDARD_MANUAL_NAME: Forest Inventory - Current Forest Data (Web Version- 2016)
COMMENT: Cycle 3. This version of the forest inventory is a combination of Interpretation Cycles 2 and 3 with additional updates based on satellite imagery and field data. This data is dynamic and different areas of the province are in different stages of completion. This version of data is updated as work in individual counties is completed. Photography years: 1995-Present. Cape Breton, Richmond, Inverness and Victoria counties updated June 2015. All counties now contain VOLUME, BASAL AREA and AVERAGE DIAMETER attribute data. Please refer to the metadata for more information.
